<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Sunder1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Sunder,</orth> subst. <emph>in s.</emph> == in two: <emph>who</emph> (the pillow) <cit><quote>seems to part in s., swelling on either side,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 388" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 388</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>gnawing my bonds in s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 5.249" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 249</bibl></cit> (F<hi rend="sub">2.3.4</hi> <emph>asunder</emph>). <cit><quote>cut my lace in s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 34</bibl></cit> (Ff <emph>asunder</emph>).
